{"tid":955754,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"首 席 韓 流 天 王 Rain 回 春 變 小 鮮 肉","createTime":"2018-12-25T16:20:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T17:46:27.000Z","uid":215823,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"05cb919ca632beadf23e4cd3d98f069f62697daf","tid":955754,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T16:20:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/26/002027_d65b77c632269070720ce575afe819a0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F26%2F002027_d65b77c632269070720ce575afe819a0.png&h=8c193eb7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/26/002029_0192cc4af8a479cf83299a84208eb5e4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F26%2F002029_0192cc4af8a479cf83299a84208eb5e4.png&h=b3bfb64b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說PSY喺聖誕前夕開騷，前日一場就邀得Rain做表演嘉賓，Rain喺現場又唱又跳，好不落力，令粉絲都非常投入，就連著名美食家盧熙英都有去捧場，佢仲趁機喺後台同Rain及PSY合照，不過照片一公開後，網民都大感驚訝，事關Rain好似暴瘦不少，仲即時回春不少，啲皮膚又嫩又滑，即時變成小鮮肉咁。"},{"pid":"02b6d24baebf0fe80b97818bdde5b9ff8fd42be8","tid":955754,"uid":76098,"like":19,"dislike":5,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T16:26:25.000Z","msg":"得罪講句 好柒"},{"pid":"3d164b3710d77b904c46f82fee46ed411e871d53","tid":955754,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02b6d24baebf0fe80b97818bdde5b9ff8fd42be8","tid":955754,"uid":76098,"like":19,"dislike":5,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T16:26:25.000Z","msg":"得罪講句 好柒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T16:27:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca7c649d28b157c881463997c967981fa7ee740","tid":955754,"uid":169381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T16:29:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b836f9035f539f1898d11fe0899abdba7af8dbcf","tid":955754,"uid":81598,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyT